      <span class="kd">protected</span> <span class="kd">abstract</span> <span class="kt">void</span> <span class="nf">onHandleIntent</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nd">@Nullable</span> <span class="nc">Intent</span> <span class="n">intent</span><span class="o">);</span>
<span class="o">}</span>
</pre></td></tr></tbody></table></code></pre></div></div>

<h4 id="自己的理解">自己的理解：</h4>

<ol>
  <li>新建Thread HandlerThread；</li>
  <li>指定ServiceHandler运行在HandlerThread中；👈关键点</li>
  <li>onStartCommand接收到消息全都send到ServiceHandler中；</li>
  <li>ServiceHandler在新线程中handleMessage然后调用onHandleIntent;</li>
</ol>
:ET